reviewText: This items gives some insight to the life of Earl but not as much as I would have liked but over-all a good item to have because I couldn't find anything else out there.

Very professional job on this video of Earl Campbell highlights.  Great action clips from his years at U.T. and with the Houston Oilers.  Good interviews with many of Earl's buddies including Bum Phillips, Willie Nelson, Dan Pastorini,various coaches & the late Howard Cosell.  Very good picture quality and sound throughout.
